  "text": "The structure of such a piecewise controller is shown in Figure 1 . Once the look-up table of local laws is available, an efficient positioning mechanism (based on a search tree) can be constructed such that the on-line evaluation routine can find the optimal control action [CITATION_1] . The effective implementation follows the scheme in Figure. 1. ",
